**[Terraform Refactoring Tip (server.tf)]**
```hcl
data "ncloud_server_image" "ubuntu" {
  filter {
    name   = "product_name"
    values = ["ubuntu-24.04"]
    regex  = true
  }
}
```
Cloud vendor API codes change frequently. Always use the `data` block to dynamically query the latest compatible spec at runtime; this is the core of IaC.
